quran[18]{c,v,t}:
  7,109,"Babategetsi bo mu bantu bo kwa Fir’auni baciye bavuga bati:- mu vy’ukuri uyu n’umurozi abufitiye ubumenyi"
  7,110,"Ashaka kubakura mugisagara canyu, none mwebwe mubivuga ko iki"
  7,111,"Bavuga bati:- nimu mureke gatoyi hamwe na mwene wabo hanyuma mubarungike abakoranye abantu bo mugisagara"
  7,112,Bakuzanire abarozi bose bafise ubumenyi bwukuroga
  7,113,"Baraje abarozi bose bokwa Fir’auni bavuga bati:- mbega turaronka impembo nitwatsinda"
  7,114,"Fir’auni aremera ati:- egome, namwe ntankeka muzoba muri mubari hafi yanje"
  7,115,"Baca bavuga bati:- ewe Mussa (iii) mbega ni wewe utangura kujugunya ubwo burozi bwawe imbere y’abantu babubone canke tuzoba ari twebwe bambere dutangura kujugunya"
  7,116,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) abishura ati:- nimujugunye mwebwe, mugihe bajugunya baciye bahumishwa amaso y’abantu bose nukubatera ubwoba nukuzana uburozi buniniya buhanitse"
  7,117,"Duca tumurungikira ubutumwa intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) duti:- nute iyo nkoni yawe, mu mwanya ica iramiragura ivyo bagize babarozi vyose"
  7,118,"Ukuri kuba kurahagaze, bica birononekara ivyo bahora bagira"
  7,119,"Kuri ivyo rero batsindiwe ngaho, nukuba mu bantu batetewe"
  7,120,N’abarozi barahindura bashira imitwe yabo hasi
  7,121,"Bavuze bati:- twebwe turemeye Umuremyi w’ibiremwa vyose"
  7,122,Umuremyi w’intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) na Haruna (iii)
  7,123,"Fir’auni\tavuga\tati:-\tyoh!\tmuramwemeye\timbere\tyuko\tntarabaha uruhusha, iyi niyo ngeso mwagiriye mugisagara mwebwe hamwe na Mussa (iii) kugira ngo mubakureho bonyene muri ico gisagara, hanyuma muce musigara muri ico gisagara mwenyene mugabo muzo bimenya ico nzobakorera"
  7,124,"Ningombwa\tndabacagagure\tamaboko\tyanyu\tn’amaguru\tyanyu ndabitandukanije, hanyuma nce ndababamba mwese kumisaraba"
  7,125,"Nabo bishura bati:- twebwe tuzosubira ku Muremyi wacu"
  7,126,"Na wewe ntiwabonye inabi iyariyo yose atari uko twemeye amajambo y’Umuremyi wacu matagatifu mugihe yadushikira, Muremyi wacu! n’uduhundire ukwihangana kwacu, kandi tukwitabe natwe turi aba Isilamu"